_:N39387564a3a94f65bc1f5326c80066a6 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Blair McDougall was appointed Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State in the Department for Business and Trade on 7 September 2025. He was elected as the MP for East Renfrewshire in July 2024.</p>\n" .
